---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title='Full-Stack Web Developer'>
	<article class='content'>
		<h1 class='title'>Brandon Martin</h1>
		<h2 class='subtitle h4'>
			Full-Stack Web Developer
		</h2>
		<p>
			I've been building for the web since 2014 — crafting fast, accessible,
			and well-architected applications from concept to deployment.
		</p>
		<p>
			My experience spans <strong>Laravel + Vue</strong> for full-stack SaaS apps,
			<strong>React</strong> for dynamic frontends, and <strong>.NET</strong>
			for robust backend services. I care about clean code, thoughtful UX,
			and shipping products that make a real difference.
		</p>
		<p>
			I'm currently exploring new roles. If you think I'd be a fit for your team,
			message me on
			<a href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/brandon-martin' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>LinkedIn</a>
			or <a href='mailto:brandon.martin101@gmail.com'>send an email</a>.
		</p>
	</article>

	<style>
		.title {
			margin-top: 3rem;
		}
		.subtitle {
			margin-bottom: 3rem;
		}
		p {
			max-width: 600px;
			margin: 1rem auto;
			line-height: 1.7;
			text-align: left;
		}
	</style>
</PageLayout>
